data.description: Come Home for the Holidays to this Beautiful Perry Home in Woodforest with large corner lot! Huge backyard for adding a Pool! Owners retreat downstairs with En-suite bath with large closets, separate shower and tub. Large Family room open to kitchen and Breakfast area. Off kitchen/walk in pantry is Half Bath. Also downstairs are the office, study, formal dining or formal living area. All downstairs is  Tile or vinyl plank waterproof flooring! Utility room in home. Upstairs to 3 bedrooms and large game room and a full bath.  Exceptional Stewart Elementary in Conroe ISD for your kids. FHA, VA and conventional loan programs!  Woodforest is a wonderful master-planned community with numerous parks, two pools, splash pads, trails, tennis, basketball courts, shopping center, restaurants and more! Walk to school and parks!
